cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with dialog control using recurrent neural networks. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) because it uses deep reinforcement learning and policy gradient methods to optimize the dialog policy. Additionally, it could belong to cs.SD (Software Engineering) because it involves developing efficient algorithms for dialog control, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) because it uses neural networks for representation learning.
